# RemindGo Pro – Roadmap

## Milestones

- [ ] M0 – Android project set up (package name, empty home screen, logging)
- [ ] M1 – Permission flow (location, activity, notifications)
- [ ] M2 – Activity Recognition + “Driving Mode” state (no geofences yet)
- [ ] M3 – Basic Tier A geofence demo with mock zone
- [ ] M4 – Tier B: entry points + polygon-confirm skeleton
- [ ] M5 – Reminder engine (deferred reminders after drive end)
- [ ] M6 – Weekly dataset refresh + local storage

## Current Focus
- M0: Set up empty Android app + clean structure.

